Class PageResponse

java.lang.Object
com.algonquin.www.model.PageResponse
Direct Known Subclasses:
LogSearchResponse, VehicleMaintenanceSearchResponse, VehicleSearchResponse
public class PageResponse extends Object
Model representing pagination response metadata.

Contains details about the current page number, page size, and total number of records.
